title: Gold 4 ranked 5s team looking for mid laner
body:
Hey guys, looking for a mid laner for our ranked 5s team, we're currently gold 4 and looking to climb.
Would prefer if you could play meta champs and can use mumble. Prefer gold or higher ranking.
WA/Perth highly preferred.
Add me in game: Faetal.

replies.body: I would love to try out for the team I'm in gold 5 and love to play pro league one day.
